data.description: Close to the main entrance to Dahlgren, Walmart, Shopping and the Harry Nice Bridge make this home a commuting dream. Featuring a rocking chair front porch. open floor plan and so much more. Welcome your guest into the large family room with vaulted ceilings . Large open kitchen with breakfast nook for dining.  Primary bedroom with ensuite bath. 2 generous sized bedrooms and hall bath round out the main floor. Home features solar panels for saving on your electric bill and is wired for a whole house generator. There is a fenced  backyard  and shed for added storage. A oversized 2 garage garage checks off your must have list. Convenient location, great condition, energy saving solar and 2 car garage make this a must see.
